  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParseTreeVisitor
    public class ParseTreeWriter
extends AbstractParseTreeVisitor
    This class implements a visitor that writes parse trees in the expression language.

        public void setStringMode​(boolean stringMode)

        Parameters:
